# NAME: ForeignMedia
# AUTHOR: steak
# TYPE: Quantumult X Filter
# DESCRIPTION: Twitch / Hulu / HBO Max / Prime Video / Peacock / Paramount+ / ESPN / BBC iPlayer 等国外媒体规则
# SOURCE: Split from GlobalServices.list
# UPDATED: 2026-05-11
#
# ================================
# 使用说明
# ================================
# 1. 文件名：ForeignMedia.list
# 2. 适用于：Quantumult X [filter_remote]
# 3. 策略组名称：国外媒体
# 4. 本文件由原 GlobalServices.list 拆分，便于后续单独维护
# 5. IP-CIDR / IP6-CIDR 已追加 no-resolve
#
# QX 远程订阅示例：
# https://raw.githubusercontent.com/reverie1988/QX/refs/heads/main/Rules/ForeignMedia.list, tag=ForeignMedia, force-policy=国外媒体, update-interval=172800, opt-parser=false, enabled=true
#
# ================================
# 规则统计
# ================================
# HOST: 0
# HOST-SUFFIX: 39
# HOST-KEYWORD: 4
# USER-AGENT: 0
# IP-CIDR: 0
# IP6-CIDR: 0
# IP-ASN: 0
# TOTAL: 43
#
# ================================
# 规则内容
# ================================
# 国外媒体
# ================================

# Twitch
HOST-SUFFIX,twitch.tv,国外媒体
HOST-SUFFIX,twitchcdn.net,国外媒体
HOST-SUFFIX,ttvnw.net,国外媒体
HOST-SUFFIX,jtvnw.net,国外媒体
HOST-SUFFIX,ext-twitch.tv,国外媒体
HOST-SUFFIX,twitchsvc.net,国外媒体
HOST-KEYWORD,twitch,国外媒体

# Hulu
HOST-SUFFIX,hulu.com,国外媒体
HOST-SUFFIX,huluim.com,国外媒体
HOST-SUFFIX,hulustream.com,国外媒体
HOST-SUFFIX,huluad.com,国外媒体
HOST-SUFFIX,hulumail.com,国外媒体
HOST-KEYWORD,hulu,国外媒体

# HBO / Max
